data.description: Explore the charm of this stunning 3-bedroom home in the sought-after Mustang school district! Conveniently situated near shopping and interstates, this residence is poised for a new owner. Step inside to discover an inviting open layout, complemented by wood-look ceramic tiles throughout the home. With a well-designed split floor plan offering ample closet space and a kitchen boasting a handy pantry, convenience is key. Outside, the spacious backyard is perfect for all your entertaining desires
